s page → new product\t2 min\tDuplicate structure Swap headline, subhead, product name\t5 min\tCustomized copy Replace product image/mockup\t2 min\tVisual update Adjust pricing/checkout button\t1 min\tReady to publish Total per product page\t~10 min\tProduction-ready UPSELL/DOWNSELL UNIVERSAL STRUCTURE Since upsells and downsells follow a predictable formula, you only need 1 master template each: Universal Upsell Template (1 Credit) Section\tElement\tDrag-Drop Customization 1\t\"Wait! Your order is not complete\" header\tChange product name 2\tOne-time offer badge + countdown timer\tAdjust timer 3\tProduct image/mockup\tSwap image 4\tValue stack (what's included)\tEdit bullet points 5\tPrice anchor ($297 value → $47 today)\tChange numbers 6\tOne-click \"Yes, Add This!\" CTA\tLink to product 7\t\"No thanks\" decline link\tLink to downsell Universal Downsell Template (1 Credit) Section\tElement\tDrag-Drop Customization 1\t\"Before you go...\" header\tChange product name 2\tReduced offer explanation\tEdit copy 3\tSmaller product bundle/lite version\tSwap image 4\tEven lower price point\tChange numbers 5\tFinal urgency element\tKeep or adjust 6\tAccept/Decline CTAs\tLink appropriately 50-OFFER PRODUCTION TIMELINE Phase\tWhat\tCredits\tTime\tDeliverable Day 1\tAI-generate 6 niche sales page masters\t6\t2 hrs\t6 templates Day 1\tAI-generate 1 upsell + 1 downsell master\t2\t30 min\t2 templates Day 1\tSave all CRO sections as My Blocks\t0\t1 hr\tReusable library Day 2-3\tClone + customize 44 sales pages\t0\t~8 hrs\t50 sales pages Day 4\tClone + customize 50 upsell pages\t0\t~4 hrs\t50 upsells Day 5\tClone + customize 50 downsell pages\t0\t~4 hrs\t50 downsells Day 6\tConnect webhooks + test flows\t0\t2 hrs\tLive funnels TOTAL\t\t8 credits\t~22 hrs\t150 pages MY BLOCKS LIBRARY TO SAVE (Day 1) Save these from your AI-generated masters for instant reuse: Block Name\tSource\tReuse Hero-Headline-Timer\tSales page header\tAll 50 sales pages Pain-Agitate-Solution\tSales page body\tA